'''otaku'''  (''plural:'' '''[[otaku]]''')
# In Japanese culture, a derogatory term for an extremely obsessed person. That obsession can be for anything such as anime, computers, celebrities, etc.
# In Western culture, not so much a derogatory term as a teasing term. Sometimes self-applied by anime's more extreme fans.
Note: In general, it's better to avoid the use of this word as the term is very derogatory in Japan.

